msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/date"
msgid "September 25th, 1944 · Carpatian mountains, Belgrade region, Yugoslavia"
msgstr ""
"25 de septiembre de 1944 - Montañas de los cárpatos, Belgrado, Yugoslavia"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/name"
msgid "Carpathian Turmoil <c(a655af)>[DLC]</c>"
msgstr "Líos en los Cárpatos <c(a655af)>[DLC]</c>"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/name_big"
msgid "Carpathian Turmoil"
msgstr "Líos en los Cárpatos"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/narrator/01"
msgid "Hmmm. These views are too peaceful... Where is our garrison?"
msgstr ""
"Hmmm. Estas vistas son demasiado tranquilas... ¿Dónde está nuestra "
"guarnición?"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/narrator/02"
msgid ""
"I'm certain that something has happened to our soldiers defending the "
"checkpoint, smells like Yugoslav partisans."
msgstr ""
"Estoy seguro de que algo les ha pasado a nuestros soldados que defienden la "
"encrucijada, me huele a partisanos yugoslavos."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/narrator/03"
msgid ""
"We first need to establish contact with the Gebirgsjäger unit and make sure "
"the checkpoint is safe. Be cautious, both the Yugoslav partisans and the "
"forward elements of the Red Army are active in the area."
msgstr ""
"Primero tenemos que establecer contacto con la unidad Gebirgsjäger y "
"asegurarnos de que encrucijada está asegurada. Tened cuidado, tanto los "
"partisanos yugoslavos como el Ejército Rojo están activos en la zona, "
"pisándonos los talones"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/narrator/04"
msgid "Damn it! Partisans spotted! They know we're here, give them hell!"
msgstr ""
"¡Maldita sea! ¡Partisanos a la vista! Saben que estamos aquí, ¡A por ellos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/narrator/05"
msgid ""
"There is no time to mess around. There are many units undergoing evacuation, "
"unite forces and work together to secure this area for the arrival of our "
"forces!"
msgstr ""
"No hay tiempo que perder. Hay muchas unidades siendo evacuadas, ¡unid "
"fuerzas y trabajad juntos para conseguir el control esta zona antes de que "
"lleguen nuestros convoyes!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/narrator/06"
msgid ""
"Good job, Soldaten! The checkpoint is ours. This is a strategic location "
"which oversees the entire valley. We must keep it under our control at all "
"costs!"
msgstr ""
"¡Buen trabajo, Soldados! La encrucijada es nuestra. Este es un lugar "
"estratégico que supervisa todo el valle. ¡Debemos mantenerlo bajo nuestro "
"control a toda costa!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/narrator/07"
msgid ""
"Gentlemen, one of our supply evacuation convoys has arrived to the valley. "
"They need to be escorted to the extraction point southward."
msgstr ""
"Caballeros, uno de nuestros convoyes de evacuación de suministros ha llegado "
"al valle. Necesitan ser escoltados al punto de extracción en el sur."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/narrator/08"
msgid ""
"Take them to their destination and keep them safe from the enemy ambushes! "
"We know both Soviet and Yugoslavian forces are active in the area!"
msgstr ""
"¡Llévadlos a su destino y mantenedlos a salvo de las emboscadas enemigas! "
"¡Sabemos que tanto las fuerzas soviéticas como las yugoslavas están activas "
"por la zona!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/narrator/09"
msgid ""
"Our supply vehicles are overloaded to the brim! With this much weight, they "
"can only reliably travel on roads. "
msgstr ""
"Nuestros vehículos de abastecimiento están sobrecargados a tope… Con tanto "
"peso, sólo pueden circular por las carreteras"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/narrator/10"
msgid ""
"The Allied bombers are pummeling the infrastructure! The bridges are getting "
"bombed to hell!"
msgstr ""
"¡Los bombarderos aliados están lanzando bombas! ¡Los puentes parecen ser su "
"objetivo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/narrator/11"
msgid "Soviets! There are enemy Soviet troops in the mix, too!"
msgstr "¡Soviéticos! ¡También hay tropas soviéticas enemigas involucradas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/narrator/12"
msgid ""
"Excellent work. The supplies are on their way to safety. Now our priority "
"must be to keep their rearguard safe. The Soviets are pressing behind us, we "
"will hold them back!"
msgstr ""
"Excelente trabajo. Los suministros están en camino a buen puerto. Ahora "
"nuestra prioridad debe ser mantener su retaguardia a salvo. Los soviéticos "
"están presionándonos por detrás- ¡los retendremos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/narrator/13"
msgid ""
"The last remnants of our armoured columns have entered the perimeter. Take "
"command of those forces and keep the soviets busy until our transports are "
"safe! Defend the central checkpoint at all costs!"
msgstr ""
"Los últimos integrantes de nuestras columnas blindadas han entrado en el "
"valle. ¡Toma el mando de esas fuerzas y mantén a los soviéticos ocupados "
"hasta que nuestros transportes estén a salvo! ¡Defiende la encruzijada toda "
"costa!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/narrator_gebirgs/01"
msgid ""
"Brandenburger! We are glad to see you are safe and sound! The Yugoslav "
"partisans have taken the checkpoint, and we lost our commanding officer!"
msgstr ""
"¡Brandenburger! ¡Nos alegra ver que estáis sanos y salvos! ¡Los partisanos "
"yugoslavos han tomado la encruzijada, nos han emboscado y hemos perdido a "
"nuestro oficial al mando!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/narrator_gebirgs/02"
msgid "Attention! I hear something... I think we have bombers overhead!"
msgstr "¡Atención! Oigo algo... ¡Creo que tenemos bombarderos sobrevolandonos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/narrator_gebirgs/03"
msgid "Dust on the horizon! Mobilized troops coming in from the south-east!"
msgstr ""
"¡Cortina de polvo en el horizonte! ¡Tropas con vehículos están llegando "
"desde el sureste!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/obj_progress"
msgid "%1% out of 3 trucks have been delivered to the extraction point."
msgstr "%1% de 3 semiorugas han sido entregados en el punto de extracción."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"That was close! You have shown your leadership, guiding your troops to "
"safety. Maybe it’s not your style to retreat, but at least we live to fight "
"another day. Now, we must get back to our own lines somehow."
msgstr ""
"¡Ha estado reñido! Has demostrado tu liderazgo, guiando a tus tropas del "
"peligro hacia a un lugar seguro. Tal vez la retirada no sea lo ideal, pero "
"al menos vivimos para luchar otro día. Ahora, debemos reagruparnos y "
"continuar la lucha."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"This is a bitter defeat. We lost a lot of lives and valuable equipment. "
"Also, the division’s re- grouping orders can’t be fulfilled anymore. The "
"march on Belgrade is going to be too easy for the Soviets! "
msgstr ""
"Esta es una amarga derrota. Hemos perdido muchas vidas y material valioso. "
"Además, las órdenes de reagrupar la división ya no se pueden cumplir. ¡Los "
"soviéticos nos aplastarán en Belgrado sin que podamos hacer nada al respecto!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/place"
msgid "Remnants of army group F"
msgstr "Restos del grupo de ejército F"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/story"
msgid " The German army in Yugoslavia is in trouble. Bulgaria and Romania are no longer allies, and the Soviet offensive puts them under high pressure. Not only that, but all over Yugoslavia they are up against Tito’s Yugoslav partisans as well. The Soviet offensive starts with a fast move across the Danube, splitting the main German force in two. With resistance and attacks on all sides, fighting becomes increasingly difficult. All the action is around German units that are desperately trying to escape the squeeze everywhere, trying to get to the south and to friendly territory.\n\n In this mission, you will be in charge of clearing the bridges across the river Olt. Advance and take the area around the bridges. Hold the area until our trucks arrive from the north. Guide them to safety, which is on the road all the way to the south where it leaves the sector. Regardless of what happens, your objective is to get the majority of your troops out of here in one piece.  \n\nGood luck!"
msgstr ""
"El ejército alemán en Yugoslavia se encuentra en un\n"
"\n"
"apuro. Bulgaria y Rumanía ya no son aliadas, y la\n"
"\n"
"Ofensiva soviética es incesante. No sólo eso,\n"
"\n"
"sino que en toda Yugoslavia los partisanos\n"
"\n"
"de Tito también causan estragos a la Wehrmacht.\n"
"\n"
"La ofensiva soviética comienza con un rápido avance por el\n"
"\n"
"Danubio, dividiendo la fuerza principal alemana en dos.\n"
"\n"
"La lucha se vuelve cada vez más difícil.\n"
"\n"
"Toda la acción se desarrolla en torno a las unidades alemanas\n"
"\n"
"Atrapadas, que desesperadamente intentan escapar,\n"
"\n"
"tratando de llegar al sur a territorio amigo.\n"
"\n"
" \n"
"\n"
"En esta misión, estarás a cargo\n"
"\n"
"de despejar los puentes que cruzan el río Olt.  \n"
"\n"
"Avanza y asegura la zona en torno a los puentes.\n"
"\n"
"Mantén el control hasta que lleguen los convoyes.\n"
"\n"
"Guíalos hacia el sur.\n"
"\n"
"Pase lo que pase, tu objetivo es conseguir\n"
"\n"
"que la mayoría de sus tropas fuera de aquí de una pieza.  \n"
"\n"
"¡Buena suerte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/task1"
msgid "Rendez- vouz the Gebirgsjäger and Brandenburger units"
msgstr "Reagrúpa las unidades Gebirgsjäger y Brandenburger"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/task2"
msgid "Secure the crossroads checkpoint"
msgstr "Toma el control de la encrucijada"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/task3"
msgid ""
"Safely evacuate the transport convoy to their destination. At least three "
"trucks must make it through."
msgstr ""
"Escolta el convoy de suministros a su destino. Al menos tres semiorugas "
"deben conseguir llegar."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/task4"
msgid "Defend the checkpoint from the Red Army assault."
msgstr "Defiende la encruzijada del asalto del Ejército Rojo."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/task_sec1"
msgid "Secret Objective #1"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto nº 1"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/task_sec1_complete"
msgid "Secret Objective #1: Find the partisan hideout."
msgstr "Objetivo secreto nº 1: Encontrar el escondite de los partisanos."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/task_sec2"
msgid "Secret Objective #2"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto nº 2"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/task_sec2_complete"
msgid "Secret Objective #2: Find the underground mining tunnels"
msgstr "Objetivo secreto nº 2: Encontrar los túneles mineros subterráneos"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger/1944_09_yugoslavia/timer"
msgid "Hold the checkpoint until our transports get to safety:"
msgstr ""
"Mantén el control de la encrucijada hasta que nuestros transportes estén a "
"salvo:"
